Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That little girl shouldn't be able\Nto move anymore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Grandma controlling her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, she wouldn't be able to make\Nsuch complicated movements{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in her condition...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That little girl...\Nis moving under her own will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is it she can move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I nailed her with my poison.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I used an antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you... get such a thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When I made the antidote for Kankuro\Nin the Village Hidden in the Sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never imagined I'd find this many\N medicinal herbs{\i0} {\i1}here in the Hidden Sand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, it's quite difficult to grow\Nmedicinal herbs in this type of location.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We only have a small amount\Nof Scurvy Grass in particular...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, this is more than enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can make three doses of antidote.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to make just three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I used one of them to heal Kankuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should be all right now, I think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just lie there and rest for a while without\N moving{\i0} {\i1}until the numbness goes away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the enemy would use poison,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I made the other two into injections\Nand brought them with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that's how...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I used one of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the effects of the antidote\Nwill only last around three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how often I get hit\Nwith poison during that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the effects of the medicine will turn\Nall of it into harmless proteins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let Sasori find out\Nthat I had this antidote...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd have an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,after he revealed his final intentions\Nand let his guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I couldn't use it until\Nthe very last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's only one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will hand this over to you,\NGranny Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me\Nthe poison was neutralized...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to live that badly,\NI won't finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that poison will kill you\Nin less than three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me they analyzed the components\Nusing the poison from back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that couldn't be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if by some chance they were able\Nto analyze the components,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they shouldn't be able to\Nmake an antidote that easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The concoction of an antidote\Nis so difficult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that even the slightest mistake\Nis not permissible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I, who made the poison,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}needed a ratio chart\Nfor its concoction...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll heal you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now poison won't affect me for\Nthe next three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything depends on\Nthose three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grandma, huh...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'm the one who knows\Nthe level of medical ability{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the Hidden Sand more\Nthan anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made a poison that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even she wouldn't be able to\Nimmediately create an antidote for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this kid's also\Na Medical Ninja, huh...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I recall, she's from the Leaf...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The current Leaf Hokage Tsunade\Nis known as a top-notch Medical Ninja...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...\Nshe made the antidote...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:08.47,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(665,620)}Three Minutes Between\NLife and Death\N\N \N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, my left hand's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here I go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Incredible strength...evasion...\Nheals wounds...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all utilize a considerable amount\Nof Chakra...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's probably already reached\Nher limit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to show my face\Nto my man Sasori...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to use the rest of\Nmy Detonation Clay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and show him that I'm a real artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get that Copy Ninja\Nout of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a little time,\Nbut how about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the bird-type from earlier,\Nthese are sure small...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that so they won't get picked off\Nby shuriken...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this amount...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Judging from the size\Nof their hind legs...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd bet their special skill\Nis jumping strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I guess we'll go with\Na battle of speed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too slow, Kakashi Sensei!\NI'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything reckless\Non your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This might be a bit of a problem...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the time being,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I stopped the bleeding\Nof the large wounds...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll use all of my remaining Chakra\Nto attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't finish this during\Nthe next three minutes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there won't be a next time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The effects of the antidote\Nwill last three minutes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you fight right away,\NGranny Chiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this isn't the time to have\Na staring contest with these things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I leave Naruto on his own,\Nhe could lose control at any moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So by maintaining a fixed distance\Nequal to how far I retreat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they're preventing me from\Nbreaking through...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If so...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'd...better be following me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Kakashi Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now at last, it's just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scowl like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I'm going to the trouble of\Nletting you see your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah-yeah, as a fellow Jinchuriki,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't keep your cool, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Gaara...back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, and I was totally convinced\Nthat you'd died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it wasn't the real me\Nthat blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, you'd better figure out\Nhow to get them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell the difference between\Na real body and a Shadow Clone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If  there's a next time, that is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We'll definitely get Gaara back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori's gonna get mad at me again\Nfor not being prepared enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not my style to think about every\N little detail and always be perfectly prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dealing with matters with a flexible\N mindset, no matter what the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to developing sophistication\Nas an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not accustomed to\Nthat kind of enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, he's a long-range type,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the worst match for someone like you,\Nwho specializes in close-range battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only two ways to\Ndefeat this type of enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One is to draw the enemy into a\N close-range fight and defeat them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The other is to outdo the enemy\Nwith a long-range attack
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But, how do we do that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter which method is taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,your unit needs either a comrade\Nwho specializes in long-range attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or one who can use support Ninjutsu\Nfor long-range battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In the event of having neither...\Nit's impossible to defeat the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be different if you were\N as smart as Shikamaru, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then what about\Nyou Kakashi Sensei...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A Jonin who's as smart as Shikamaru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and possesses support Ninjutsu\Nfor long-range battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we've got what we need!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should get right to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't work out that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't leave himself open\Nif we just chase him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, you're in range!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He infiltrated the Hidden Sand\N by himself and defeated Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And most important...\Nhe's a member of the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this isn't the time for me\Nto be taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is create\Nan opening from our end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were able to catch on to what I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,then lend me an ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heh... I'll admit it.\NYou're an impressive kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who would've thought she could destroy\Nthe Third Kazekage...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's useless to use\Nother Human Puppets any longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't used this since\NI joined the Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember when that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't aged at all since\Nhe left my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's exactly the same as before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really been a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,since I used myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,into a Human Puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If his entire body is a puppet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then it's safe to assume{\i0} {\i1}all of the weapons \Ninside his body are covered with poison...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's already been over a minute\Nsince I gave myself the antidote shot...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to finish me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to attack me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The effects of the antidote\Nwill last less than two minutes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}During that time...{\i0} {\i1}somehow, I need to turn this\N into a close-range battle{\i0} {\i1}and then finish him off...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make the first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... what will you do?
